<br>
As far as Gaia goes, if you will look back in the posts, you will find one called &quot;Scrolls from the Oracle&quot;.  The first few of those should have to do with Gaia.  I can't remember if I want back to Gaia or not.  But it won't hurt to read them.  Those are straight out of The Idiot's Guide to Classical Mythology&quot;.  <br>
<br>
